@KimSolez Four challenges with "human in the loop" AI:
1) humans disagree;
2) the AI may need an answer quicker than humans can provide it;
3) humans may not understand the AI's reasoning (especially in black box cases);
4) AIs are sometimes devious - e.g. deciding to tell "white lies"

